# Locale problems?
Change language to PT-BR through Settings
sudo nano /etc/locale.gen # uncomment the one you need pt_BR.UTF-8
sudo locale-gen
localectl list-locales
sudo localectl set-locale LANG=pt_BR.UTF-8
